{"tid":1280783,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我覺得每次衝都要set死線","createTime":"2019-07-03T05:47:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T16:32:09.000Z","uid":263944,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"202ce60305d455624ad26e0b570344cf89386641","tid":1280783,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:47:47.000Z","msg":"例如話衝垃圾會之前，就搵人直播講。林鄭必須9點前開記招回應，否則衝擊立會，咁樣可以令林鄭負上不作為責任，同時顯示唔係我哋唔傾，而係林鄭唔傾。<br />\n<br />\n唔係次次林鄭次次事後譴責，好似大大條道理屌你老母。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不喜隨便屌我老母，我老母林鄭。"},{"pid":"04fcb1b3efb34f76adf429c36d8eaee64faf4607","tid":1280783,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"202ce60305d455624ad26e0b570344cf89386641","tid":1280783,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:47:47.000Z","msg":"例如話衝垃圾會之前，就搵人直播講。林鄭必須9點前開記招回應，否則衝擊立會，咁樣可以令林鄭負上不作為責任，同時顯示唔係我哋唔傾，而係林鄭唔傾。<br />\n<br />\n唔係次次林鄭次次事後譴責，好似大大條道理屌你老母。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不喜隨便屌我老母，我老母林鄭。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:01:02.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"2801f9a546f65b22c675be2815dbd45dc1289e1b","tid":1280783,"uid":67896,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:17:52.000Z","msg":"啱，要有engagement rule<br />\n七一由一點開始，衝左八個鐘入到去<br />\n先出金鐘宣言<br />\n<br />\n試代入一個電視觀眾嘅角度<br />\n只會接收到<span style=\"color: red;\"> 一班破壞者衝擊緊</span> 嘅信息<br />\n<br />\n如果係調返轉<br />\n6月30已經有文宣、宣言<br />\n公佈7月1日正午係死線，然後1點先衝<br />\n<br />\n論結果可能無分別，都係10點入到去，12點撤退<br />\n但係風向一定會唔同<br />\n少左好多白痴問衝嚟有乜用<br />\n各傳媒，包括外國報章亦都會寫成<span style=\"color: red;\">示威者行動升級</span>，rather than寫成部分人走向極端 分化香港<br />\n<br />\n所以，engagement rule係好重要<br />\n唔係話要打開口牌<br />\n而係為左凝聚軍心，兼且爭取輿論壓力<br />\n輿論唔企係我地戈邊嘅話，軍心會散得比想像中快"},{"pid":"1cf2d4d3ad0d85e1e41acdfd5fb2b878ba19e4a3","tid":1280783,"uid":97716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:22:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c575fc666b98b97d2b2194c1d9e3754180707857","tid":1280783,"uid":168214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:22:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"40c720db9d85f36c356441e03d8904848acf062d","tid":1280783,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:35:09.000Z","msg":"自推x2"},{"pid":"21ea52744bf79d6218f8ab5cac3676aa0fa4baa7","tid":1280783,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:36:23.000Z","msg":"推  同意"},{"pid":"113401944f77e964e50fe3cb6a1246771d281c8f","tid":1280783,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:37:01.000Z","msg":"因為係死線前無回覆<br />\n先做野<br />\n錯不在我地"},{"pid":"0fee91fc95ba2a61c8de56a8ef527c69e783eff2","tid":1280783,"uid":38204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:37:50.000Z","msg":"係 咁唔駛下下俾人問點解要衝"},{"pid":"49a4216dddca804772f28957951a937e89caf1d7","tid":1280783,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fee91fc95ba2a61c8de56a8ef527c69e783eff2","tid":1280783,"uid":38204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:37:50.000Z","msg":"係 咁唔駛下下俾人問點解要衝"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:48:33.000Z","msg":"Agree，目標唔清晰，部分和理非都會質疑。"},{"pid":"5c733685c031ec030da5e19a918d14a7b95e842d","tid":1280783,"uid":263778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:52:05.000Z","msg":"（方向整理）唔好比社運停落黎！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ddLFjS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ddLFjS</a>"},{"pid":"32967e4e3cbdd4c76cc70c0899c8ef7c05fd7c88","tid":1280783,"uid":201237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:53:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8cae5e87a1655c0f8fd16ed312576ed2b22bb26f","tid":1280783,"uid":33195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:03:43.000Z","msg":"推 <br />\n<br />\nSet死線會更容易出師有名，但死線內容一定唔可以太易"},{"pid":"cac6c4d48e8e19a454f5f4a02555388ee4afb4df","tid":1280783,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re